      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved. Whether you\u2019re just commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty handles like a dream. It's clean, dependable, and ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
