    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the S54 3.2L high-compression inline-six. This unit features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal timing and torque delivery. The chassis has undergone essential subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor pan fatigue, ensuring structural integrity during high-G cornering. Power is sent through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a M-Variable Lock differential. While the exterior shows honest road patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers for a taut, communicative ride. This is a purist\u2019s machine with a focus on drivetrain excellence and throttle response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
