      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior paint still holds a deep, mirror-like luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with plush leather seating that remains firm and supportive, showing only slight natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the adaptive cruise control, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history. The car recently passed a multi-point inspection and comes with a set of tires that have plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a high-quality driving experience without the new-car price tag. Service records are available upon request.",
